    "• CERTIFAI: The development of counterfactual explanations is the main focus of CERTIFAI (Counterfactual Explanations for Robustness, Transparency, Interpretability, and Fairness of Artificial Intelligence models) [73].",
    "Existing counterfactual generating algorithms have a few shortcomings, such as infeasible examples.",
    "It hinders the process of evaluating the robustness and fairness of developed models.",
    "This tool aims to provide a solution to this issue.",
    "9.2 Supporting datasets • HELOC [151]: The HELOC (Home Equity Line of Credit) dataset is a real-world dataset popularly known in the field of credit risk assessment and lending."
